author: stefan2
msg: On the 10Gb branch: fix a membuffer cache effectiveness issue.
The lower part of the group index was always identical to the
cache segment index. I.e. most groups would not be used at all
causing the used ones to overflow quickly.
* subversion/libsvn_subr/cache-membuffer.c
(entry_t): fix typo in docstring
(get_group_index): select group independently of segment
